      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "      3. Línea Abierta: Latinas on the Rise (2015)"
        },
        {
          "type": "link",
          "url": "https://americanarchive.org/catalog/cpb-aacip-24586416334",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "https://americanarchive.org/catalog/cpb-aacip-24586416334"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "          Listen to minutes 8:25 to 12:52; 16:06 to 21:21; 21:57 to 26:00; and 33:50 to 36:19,  where the host interviews a young, newly elected Latina     "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "         councilmember, Dulce Gutiérrez, who became one of the first Latinas to win in Yakima, Washington. She was elected with 85% of the votes.  "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
